snippet.title: Amber Heard HUGE BACKLASH! Causes DIRECTOR to turn COMMENTS off!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is officially(allegedly) hired for Aquaman 2. It is unknown if Wan is responsible for Heard staying on the project, or if it is more of a Warner Brothers "thing." Wan ended up turning the comments to his posts about the film, off, as a result of Amber Heard not being fired. 
Johnny Depp was not given a fair, equal, and/or reasonable treatment when it came to  him being fired. Depp lost his role with Warner Brothers, for Pirates of the Caribbean, AND The Fantastic Beasts series(Grindelwald.)

#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #Doctor Soup
